user_review: A wonderful little shop tucked off of Mont-Royal!  I first discovered La Mise en Place because they are a Lufa basket drop off point.  But they are so much more!  They are a caterer/weekly meal service, making up different sized portions of homecooked food for busy people.  They do a weekly ordering/basket type system, but it isn't obligatory, they also have all kinds of goodies on hand for walk ins.  They often have samples and are super friendly, they can tell you about everything that goes into any dish.
